#HaqiqatShow #Haqiqatjou #muslimskeptic 

Daniel Haqiqatjou addresses the accusations made against him by Muslim "debater" Jake Brancatella and why Brancatella has been running from Daniel's multiple debate challenges to him. Why is Jake the Muslim Metaphysician so afraid? Are his criticisms of Daniel valid or just the ignorant ramblings of a clown?

Full episode: https://www.youtube.com/live/IfI56vYp7kQ
